research_municipality_step.notes: The official City of Frost, Texas website identifies Shannon Wayman as the current Mayor. Other sources, such as the Texas Municipal League and Texas State Directory Online, list Anthony Harris as Mayor and Shannon Wayman as Mayor Pro Tem, which appears to be outdated information. Megan Welborn and Johnny Sutton are listed as Alderpersons in the Texas Municipal League and Texas State Directory Online, which is interpreted as Council Members. Juli Reeves is also listed under Government Officials in the Texas Municipal League directory, and is presumed to be a Council Member.
